{"tid":441191,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[3DS/Switch]MHXX 討論區(91) 1001 唔開post 仆街死全家","createTime":"2017-10-19T12:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T02:52:46.000Z","uid":50845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef4dd4c0745b2272c9f5c4c494485e4bd8f1d74e","tid":441191,"uid":50845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>WIKI Link<br />\n<a href=\"http://wiki.mhxg.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwiki.mhxg.org%2F&d=SFdoF744aWed7kNU3WVg7ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=ff5bb9e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://wiki.mhxg.org/</a><br />\nKEY任,前置任,素材出處係哂度<br />\n自己查完有唔明再問<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n配裝器:<br />\n<a href=\"http://mhxx.wiki-db.com/sim/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmhxx.wiki-db.com%2Fsim%2F&d=SFdoF744aWed7kNU3WVg7ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=b0adba42\" target=\"_blank\">http://mhxx.wiki-db.com/sim/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.geocities.jp/masax_mh/mhxx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.geocities.jp%2Fmasax_mh%2Fmhxx%2F&d=SFdoF744aWed7kNU3WVg7ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=78c3e223\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.geocities.jp/masax_mh/mhxx/</a><br />\n前者網頁版,後者Java版,任君選擇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n清完Key任無緊急任打點算?<br />\n禁X開個地圖望下邊度搵NPC傾記<br />\n<br />\n點捉怪?<br />\n打到隻野跛腳,放陷阱,掟捕獲玉<br />\n<br />\n點轉風格<br />\n去自己間屋個裝備箱有得轉<br />\n<br />\n點解d技能黑左?<br />\n因為個技能發動唔到,可能關你把武事<br />\n<br />\n新手用XXXXX著咩裝好?<br />\n下位鬼蛙<br />\n上位鬼蛙S<br />\nG位鬼蛙X<br />\n咩話?唔想著鬼蛙?<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n新手用開XX,整邊把武好?<br />\n上下位求其見到邊把你整到得黎又最高攻整果把用住先就得<br />\n<br />\n新手求高手帶打XXXXXXX<br />\n唔一定時時都有老手得閒帶打<br />\n開個一人一任房搵同位既獵人互相幫忙解會多d人肯入<br />\n<br />\n咩叫z順?<br />\n即係一人一任,跟個次序,舊時3ds個次序跟z字咁排<br />\n<br />\n點解我同個friend連唔到線?<br />\n一係你block柒左佢,一係你set左switch專用房佢玩3ds入唔到<br />\n<br />\n隻game點先叫爆機?<br />\n打哂村9星同解放hr 整完螳螂裝同二名裝(好似係)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>今集點刷護石？<br />\n</ins><br />\n下載任務「急募‧炭鉱採掘求ム」，<br />\n1神島3重弩秒殺碎龍交副任走人（選單第二頁尾2）<br />\n<br />\n流程（重弩手）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HpRhDZdMKZ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHpRhDZdMKZ0&d=SFdoF744aWed7kNU3WVg7ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=27fa61f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HpRhDZdMKZ0</a><br />\n補充：<br />\n回家玉之後，可以先等控手射鬼人彈加攻（都有人唔射，控手話事啦）<br />\n注意頭先係弱點，唔係角<br />\n唔使食貓飯，快啲開波仲好<br />\n<br />\n武器建議用ガオウ‧クオバルデ <a href=\"http://wiki.mhxg.org/ida/310358.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwiki.mhxg.org%2Fida%2F310358.html&d=SFdoF744aWed7kNU3WVg7ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f9c53766\" target=\"_blank\">http://wiki.mhxg.org/ida/310358.html</a><br />\n因為斬裂彈lv2 入brave mode 快<br />\n<br />\n技能：<br />\n貫通彈強化、超會心必出<br />\n再用弱特、見切加會心率<br />\n弾導強化就俾未習慣距離嘅人用<br />\n<br />\n未有裝點算好？<br />\n街場搵ブラキディオス有好多武器自由場刷住先</blockquote>"},{"pid":"197a2ce8a643ac42cf274669ad99b3490c77ae6b","tid":441191,"uid":50845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:22:58.000Z","msg":"sorry<br />\n係留code 區先啱"},{"pid":"5ca024363bc994833b0c3e93d372a66174e70c96","tid":441191,"uid":1351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:25:22.000Z","msg":"[3DS/SWITCH]MHXX討論區(91)  黑炎王係xx唔係神裝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/440508/page/8?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/440508/page/8?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你係到做乜鳩"},{"pid":"4d2178de220bc31ed6763d8782268e6e5995c056","tid":441191,"uid":50845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"sor9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e45f68051a6b5b457e541d45171c39e8c2f7600","tid":441191,"uid":17718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:02:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d57ddd270db0910